# One POSIX-ERE per line, matched against the CONNECT host. Anchored so
# `evil-anthropic.com.attacker.net` does NOT match. `*.anthropic.com` would be an INVALID regex.
(^|\.)anthropic\.com$
(^|\.)openai\.com$
(^|\.)chatgpt\.com$
# kiro (Amazon Q / Cognito + kiro.dev) — EXACT region-pinned hosts from the proxy log (Task 9), NOT a
# broad amazonaws.com glob. The q.us-east-1 regex also covers desktop-release.q.us-east-1.amazonaws.com.
(^|\.)cognito-identity\.us-east-1\.amazonaws\.com$
(^|\.)q\.us-east-1\.amazonaws\.com$
(^|\.)kiro\.dev$
